node.text: President Trump respected and LOVED American soldiers! Sleepy Joe Biden disrespects our soldiers and their sacrifices. We NEED President Trump back! 👏🏻🇺🇸

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Proud Republicans on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Jack Cummings @Jack_Top4997 Was it worth it, probably not. Did| lose my legs for nothing, looks like it. Did my mates die in vain. Yep. On my 11th Bangaversary it's a very somber one. Many emotions going through my head, anger, betrayal sadness to name a few....'.

node.text: I can’t imagine how the families of the 2,400 fallen American soldiers feel. Sleepy Joe Biden abandoned American allies and journalists in Afghanistan without a realistic plan to get them out of the country. Our “President” is embarrassing America on the world stage! 👏🏻🇺🇸
